== Popular culture == The dinosaur-themed rock act Majungas credits the inspiration behind their band name and self-titled song "Majunga" the episode "Cannibal Dinosaur", which features ''[[Majungasaurus]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Majungas|url = https://www.imdb.com/name/nm7750602/bio|website = IMDb|accessdate = 2016-01-10}}</ref>
